Package: inspercidados
Title: Access to Brazilian Urban Datasets from Insper Cidades
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Vinicius", "Reginatto", , "viniciusor@insper.edu.br", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Insper Cidades", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: A lightweight interface for discovering, downloading, and citing
    curated Brazilian urban datasets hosted on Insper's Dataverse repository.
    Provides three core functions: list_datasets() to browse available data,
    get_dataset() to download data directly into R, and cite_dataset() to
    generate properly formatted academic citations.
